title: Swiss Winter Sports - Zurich Edition pp4A5.pdf
description:
Swiss Winter Sports - Zurich Edition

This handy guide lists all the significant ski and snowboard resorts that you can reach from Zurich, with key features about each resort.

The information is a summary of more detailed information available at http://www.swisswintersports.co.uk. This comprehensive site is the most complete English-language guide to all the resorts in and around Switzerland. It provides weather and resort conditions, piste maps, travel tips, accommodation suggestions and a host of other information you will need whether you are planning a trip from within Switzerland or looking to visit Switzerland and sample the best winter sports facilities in the world.

Publication Year: 2013
